'Exercise2' directory:
	This directory is for the shell script assignment. 
	In it:
		exercise2_yixin.sh  -- shell script file
		fluxes -- a directory contains all the input data files
		monthly_prec -- a directory contains monthly mean precipitation 
				(result of problem 1)
		areal_mean_monthly_prec.txt -- areal mean of precipitation for each month
						(result of problem 2)
		other files or directories -- temporal files generated when running the shell script;
					      test files

'exercise_python' directory:
	This directory is for the python assignment. 
	In it:
		exercise_python_yixin.py  -- python script file
		fluxes -- a directory contains all the input data files
		monthly_prec -- a directory contains monthly mean precipitation
				(result of problem 1)
	        areal_mean_monthly_prec -- areal mean of precipitation for each month
					   (result of problem 2)



